catalogEntryView.shortDescription: An extra soft, extra plush sofa that comfortably seats you and your guests. Ideal for placing along far-reaching walls or corridors.
catalogEntryView.longDescription: Add tons of comfortable seating area with this extra comfortable sofa. The sofa features a simple, clean design, wide armrests, rounded cushioning, and easy to clean polyester fabric. The sofa's modern styling sits low to the ground for easy display of your favorite decor on the walls above it. No assembly required.
catalogEntryView.name: Soft Plush Sofa
